name: Bulbasaur
pokedex_description: A strange seed was planted on its back at birth. The plant sprouts and grows with this Pok√©mon.

name: Charizard
pokedex_description: Spits fire that is hot enough to melt boulders. Known to cause forest fires unintentionally.

name: Squirtle
pokedex_description: After birth, its back swells and hardens into a shell. Powerfully sprays foam from its mouth.

name: Pikachu
pokedex_description: It keeps its tail raised to monitor its surroundings. If you yank its tail, it will try to bite you.

name: Vulpix
pokedex_description: At the time of birth, it has just one tail. The tail splits from its tip as it grows older.

name: Psyduck
pokedex_description: It has mystical powers but doesn't recall that it has used them. That is why it always looks puzzled.

name: Geodude
pokedex_description: Commonly found near mountain trails, etc. If you step on one by accident, it gets angry.

name: Onix
pokedex_description: As it grows, the stone portions of its body harden to become similar to a diamond, but colored black.

name: Kingler
pokedex_description: The large pincer has 10000 hp of crushing power. However, its huge size makes it unwieldy to use.

name: Starmie
pokedex_description: Its central core glows with the seven colors of the rainbow. Some people value the core as a gem.

name: Lapras
pokedex_description: A gentle soul that can read the minds of people. It can ferry people across the sea on its back.

name: Mewtwo
pokedex_description: It was created by a scientist after years of horrific gene splicing and DNA engineering experiments.
